---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-cream-deep bg-cream-deep/40">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display text-xl font-semibold">Barker <span class="text-terracotta">&amp;</span> Bow</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-soft max-w-xs">
        Handmade dog scarves, sewn with love in small batches. Every good boy and girl deserves one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-soft">Explore</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/store" class="hover:text-terracotta">Shop scarves</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-terracotta">Our story</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-terracotta">Get in touch</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ink-soft">Follow along</p>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-terracotta">Instagram</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-terracotta">Facebook</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-terracotta">Email us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-cream-deep">
    <p class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-5 text-xs text-ink-soft">
      © {year} Barker &amp; Bow. Handmade with care.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
